{"tid":338252,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（帶飯）有冇人好驚比同事睇到自己嘅飯盒","createTime":"2017-07-28T04:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T19:03:20.000Z","uid":71166,"like":4,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9770fa696a562ad9b083412987223c9b5423dd9","tid":338252,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:41:31.000Z","msg":"帶飯嘅巴絲，會唔會好驚比同事睇到自己嘅飯盒<br />\n<br />\n因為D飯餸好亂，感覺好行酸<br />\n賣相唔好睇，D餸好少等等<br />\n我每次帶飯都好驚比人望我個飯盒<br />\n重要問我：「欣宜，咩嚟架？」<br />\n有時真係好難為情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47be7eb280a14cf4aafedef6daf4d56c4e5b6d76","tid":338252,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"入廁所食囉<br />\n<br />\n或者落樓下公園"},{"pid":"bb48f6acf743db39ff61e85b0df40b5a7df40169","tid":338252,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>入廁所食囉<br />\n<br />\n或者落樓下公園</blockquote><br />\n我今日去左雜物房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5pl7gk1e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5pl7gk1e&h=d2565311&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f52b8b2120d1907dc610c6a6288676bbc6810145","tid":338252,"uid":3244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22c3c29e989f09f5e3eb5aa32f6b4f8a83172a90","tid":338252,"uid":131706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T04:54:34.000Z","msg":"我自己會坐埋一邊自己食，唔同其他人一張枱"},{"pid":"e5433bc0bcb9f6d406369c9adb1cb18090399c55","tid":338252,"uid":27221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"試過帶營多加雞翼<br />\n比同事見到又勁大反應問問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意食咪帶 又關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0879d05e82bfee1a4d4a04c2de326d968e7fe9bf","tid":338252,"uid":42734,"lik