f8c5404547b436d40387afd5045473d078eb1","tid":338252,"uid":13367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T01:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁又確實喺有好多是非八卦精嘅，<br />\n一喺就拎去公園食，一喺就整靚啲自己個飯，<br />\n接受唔到就改變，<br />\n改變唔到就離開，<br />\n你應該唔會因為個飯而辭職呱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重點係佢去第二間公司都會帶飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db126f04c4077071db7ece5a28340af326dbb307","tid":338252,"uid":16376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:50:03.000Z","msg":"有時女朋友整得太靚個飯俾我 同事見到嘩嘩聲好尷尬"},{"pid":"e23909c682c7487f8b99e496f8e0b5131423dc91","tid":338252,"uid":16092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"寒酸"},{"pid":"f41878346927082beebb35d2a27eb122b16bcec4","tid":338252,"uid":25955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:55:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時女朋友整得太靚個飯俾我 同事見到嘩嘩聲好尷尬</blockquote><br />\n你贏左架啦"},{"pid":"dc7896b05f042e2925001156104b7fea37909eef","tid":338252,"uid":42734,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:38:32.000Z","msg":"邊個敢笑弘b個飯我打撚柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b331d9373e397be3fcd85a16fafade494cf20288","tid":338252,"uid":118721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T04:43:35.000Z","msg":"我公司d 垃圾同事都係咁<br />\n屌佢老母<br />\n我食咩關你撚事咩<br />\n又唔撚洗你食<br />\n我食得落口未得<br />\n樓主<br />\n你記住你去到邊間公司都係有哩d 打把人<br />\n你係一大張食飯枱定自己位？"},{"pid":"c21b3783036ec482ebf3b742c5506edd20669315","tid":338252,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個敢笑弘b個飯我打撚柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n褲褲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717b44bce845fa6a098d3d92b5f1df3382a4c9f4","tid":338252,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:03:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過帶營多加雞翼<br />\n比同事見到又勁大反應問問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意食咪帶 又關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲想食你呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我既話就是鳩但無所謂<br />\n喺公司食飯又唔係歎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c5be39db3480593de3a390b6843f789f6d99c2","tid":338252,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我公司d 垃圾同事都係咁<br />\n屌佢老母<br />\n我食咩關你撚事咩<br />\n又唔撚洗你食<br />\n我食得落口未得<br />\n樓主<br />\n你記住你去到邊間公司都係有哩d 打把人<br />\n你係一大張食飯枱定自己位？</blockquote><br />\n一張大桌<br />\n食咩都要佢理<br />\n外賣定帶飯都要望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲問咩黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好果餐又要望<br />\n唔好果餐又要問<br />\n到食果時又打眼色<br />\n攪到我出去食算 怕左佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca687484285a7de495f1592a745d59ea9bd060c","tid":338252,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>試過帶營多加雞翼<br />\n比同事見到又勁大反應問問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意食咪帶 又關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有啲想食你呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我既話就是鳩但無所謂<br />\n喺公司食飯又唔係歎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食乜真係關佢Q事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62be833bc04671ea43d8a4e68605f0db8c16e1f6","tid":338252,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過帶營多加雞翼<br />\n比同事見到又勁大反應問問問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n鐘意食咪帶 又關你事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係關佢Q事<br />\n又唔係佢食 又唔洗佢出錢<br />\n真係好怕班八婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我尋日呢埋雜物房食佢又眼望望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e23fa33765de9d8aaa0a664bf937de058005d83c","tid":338252,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:12:18.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}